## ğŸ” Key Insights
- Total sales exceeded the defined target, indicating strong business performance  
- Significant sales growth observed from 2020 to 2021, with stable performance in 2022  
- North America is the highest revenue-generating region  
- Accessories category has the highest profit margin  
- DAX-based time intelligence enables accurate performance comparison 
